StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetChangeRequestAtachmentsForChangeRequest]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@ChangeRequestID uniqueiden..er AS
SELECT CHANGE_REQUEST_ATTACHMENT_ID, CHANGE_REQUEST_ID, NAME, UPLOAD_DATE, UPLOADED_BY FROM [USMC].[CHANGE_REQUEST_ATTACHMENT] WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE CHANGE_REQUEST_ID = @ChangeRequestID ORDER BY UPLOAD_DATE DESC
